                        width: 1,
                      ),
                      borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(8),
                    ),
                    filled: true,
                    fillColor: FlutterFlowTheme.darkBackground,
                    contentPadding: EdgeInsets.fromLTRB(20, 24, 20, 24),
